## Assistant

<thinking>
.




</thinking>

I can see the issue. The HTML file is complex and relies on external scripts (like Three.js for the globe effect and GSAP for animations). When opened as a local file, these scripts may not load properly due to CORS restrictions or missing dependencies. Let me create a simpler, self-contained version that will render properly and then deploy it to Vercel.



**Tool Call: suite-showcase/index.html**
Status: Completed

Diff: suite-showcase/index.html
```
<file_path> plans/suite-showcase/index.html </file_path>
<edit_description> Fix HTML homepage for proper rendering </edit_description>
```

